rows.label: qev041404_MSG0001
rows.name:
Popote hear what sound like boom of fireworks,
then was suddenly flung all the way out here!
Heart of friend bleeds for suffering of Popote, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041404_MSG0002
rows.name:
...In that case, hurry up and bring coldberries and
spicy sacrifole pollen! Popote HUNGRY![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041404_MSG0003
rows.name:
*sniff* *sniff* Something smell good.
It smell of coldberries with spicy sacrifole pollen![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041404_MSG0004
rows.name: Friend found them all? Perfect! Now hand them over![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041404_MSG0005
rows.name:
*homph* *ohm nom nom* Soooo goooood! *gulp*
These berries are the best![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041404_MSG0006
rows.name: Ahhhh... Popote feel like new Nopon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041404_MSG0007
rows.name:
Now that belly of Popote full, time to head back to
caravan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041404_MSG0008
rows.name: Friend can go back to Ngogo now. So long![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041404_MSG0009
rows.name:
Pisa still not back. Work piling up at caravan.
This gross negligence of duties![ST:wait ]
